snippet.title: Ann - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1511270/Ann/
Itchio : https://rongrong.itch.io/ann
Newgrounds : https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/811907

There's a reason why no one is allowed to stay in the school at night.

The game is free! You can also play the entire game in Japanese language!  Have fun!
Special thanks to these people for helping me in the development of the game : 

Karrina S. : https://www.instagram.com/otter_ngeng/
Mazumaro : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-1J4M8x5B9d5l7_iiq1eGg
Soundtrack by : Yakikaze (Devlin Bataric) & Mandy Kowara
Sam for the Japanese translation of the game and the entire Rong Discord server.

=========================================================

Patreon : https://www.patreon.com/rongrong

More of my works and all social media links : https://linktr.ee/rong_rong
